{"tid":2245981,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"覺唔覺住官塘好低賤?","createTime":"2020-10-16T16:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T16:30:20.000Z","uid":30788,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2346797916381906c29d970ba7cb417c7eaa9d8e","tid":2245981,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:02:31.000Z","msg":"觀塘的貧窮人口為全香港最高，共有10.9萬貧窮人口。 <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"> 窮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據2016年香港中期人口統計，觀塘區的人口為648,541人[1]，為香港人口第二多的行政區。 <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">逼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n011年起《起動九龍東》計劃開始後，大批商廈重建所引起的工作人口大增，但同時欠缺規劃，令<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">交通擠塞、空氣污染</span></span>和市容問題變得嚴重。2015年環保署空氣數據，發現觀塘錄得高風險時數達344小時，升至全港第2  <br />\n<br />\n觀塘區有<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">七成</span></span>居民都是住於公營房屋或由政府興建的自置樓宇。"},{"pid":"f374e8ec561db44f3dc252998cc89ab1a7bbf09e","tid":2245981,"uid":2471,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"住梅窩低賤啲"},{"pid":"9ba2d01ba115f1ecabd1a7c25f951b4ea75ff4ab","tid":2245981,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"邊到係全港人口最多區域<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17563513b8696117d28ba907ae52a024b773d59e","tid":2245981,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:06:11.000Z","msg":"但係觀塘好多嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2eac8b154c8a94b941d63a568eda66f42453ae","tid":2245981,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f374e8ec561db44f3dc252998cc89ab1a7bbf09e","tid":2245981,"uid":2471,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"住梅窩低賤啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"你老母仲賤"},{"pid":"43a68bc3a97b0bd7dd528d6ba44983e1b5d815d6","tid":2245981,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ba